data.description: Explore this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in Larimore, ND. This ranch-style house offers a large living room addition and has original hardwood, a fireplace, 2 main floor bedrooms, bathrooms, and laundry. It also includes an attached single garage and a newer detached double garage.  The basement provides a kitchenette, living space, bathroom, and 2 bedrooms (no egress). Note: The main level Blue and Brown carpet will be replaced soon.
